title: Shrimad Ramayan
subTitle: Celebrations erupted across the kingdom of Ayodhya after the birth of Ram. Later, Shiva and Parvati arrive to bless the young prince.

title: Baal Veer
subTitle: After facing evil Baalveer's wrath, Manav and Meher walk out in shame. Meanwhile, Bhayankar Pari warns Baalveer that she will destroy Natkhat Pari.

title: Guru Aur Bhole
